<!-- Section 4: System Architecture -->
<h1 id="section4">4. System Architecture</h1>
<div class="section">
<h3>High-Level Architecture</h3>
<pre>
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                     FRONTEND (Next.js 14)                          |
|   [Videos]    [Posts]    [Calendar]    [Analytics]    [Accounts]   |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
                                |
                                v
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                    NGINX (Reverse Proxy)                           |
|           SSL/TLS  -  Rate Limiting  -  Load Balancing             |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
                                |
                                v
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                    BACKEND API (Express.js)                        |
|     [Auth]     [Videos]     [Posts]     [Analytics]    [Accounts]  |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
        |               |               |
        v               v               v
+---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+
|  PostgreSQL   | |    Redis      | |   AWS S3      |
|  (Database)   | | (Queue/Cache) | |  (Storage)    |
+---------------+ +---------------+ +---------------+
                        |
                        v
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                     QUEUE WORKERS (Bull)                           |
|   [Video Processing]   [Post Publishing]   [Analytics Sync]        |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
                                |
                                v
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                    EXTERNAL PLATFORMS                              |
|      Instagram API    -    YouTube API    -    Facebook API        |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
</pre>

<h3>Video Processing Pipeline</h3>
<ol>
<li>User uploads video via frontend</li>
<li>Original video saved to S3 (<code>videos/raw/</code>)</li>
<li>Processing job added to Bull queue</li>
<li>FFmpeg generates 6 platform-specific formats:
<ul>
<li>Instagram Reel (1080x1920, 9:16)</li>
<li>Instagram Feed (1080x1080, 1:1)</li>
<li>YouTube Short (1080x1920, 9:16)</li>
<li>YouTube Video (1920x1080, 16:9)</li>
<li>Facebook Square (1080x1080, 1:1)</li>
<li>Facebook Landscape (1920x1080, 16:9)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Thumbnails generated (1s, 3s, 5s)</li>
<li>Video status updated to READY</li>
</ol>

<h3>Publishing Flow</h3>
<ol>
<li>User creates post with video and caption</li>
<li>Post scheduled or published immediately</li>
<li>Scheduler checks every minute for due posts</li>
<li>Platform-specific service publishes video</li>
<li>Platform post ID and URL stored</li>
<li>Analytics synced every 6 hours</li>
</ol>
</div>

